1
00:00:07,061 --> 00:00:08,686
Everything's on hold till I make the announcement.
在我正式宣布之前一切都暂停，

2
00:00:09,256 --> 00:00:10,159
That's not for a few weeks.
还有几个星期.

3
00:00:11,107 --> 00:00:13,241
-Then all hell breaks loose. -Yep
-接下来所有的事情都会乱哄哄的. -Yep

4
00:00:14,599 --> 00:00:17,714
Joe, you've been doing this for two days.
Joe,这两天你一直在这样，

5
00:00:18,292 --> 00:00:19,325
Is your neck bothering you?
你是不是脖子疼?

6
00:00:20,393 --> 00:00:21,487
Maybe you should see a doctor.
也许你该去看看医生.

7
00:00:22,015 --> 00:00:23,522
You're right. If it doesn't get better soon.
你说得没错. 如果还不快点好的话，

8
00:00:24,035 --> 00:00:24,604
I'll have to have it looked at.
我就得请人看看了.

9
00:00:25,101 --> 00:00:25,966
It's probably from the train.
可能是坐火车引起的.

10
00:00:26,641 --> 00:00:27,286
What happened on the train?
火车上怎么啦?

11
00:00:27,703 --> 00:00:28,324
We went to New York.
我们上次到纽约去，

12
00:00:28,560 --> 00:00:29,391
On the way back, the train was delayed.
结果在回来的路上，火车给延误了.

13
00:00:30,333 --> 00:00:30,960
For how long?
延误了多长时间?

14
00:00:31,295 --> 00:00:34,199
Five hours. We stopped somewhere in Connecticut for five hours.
5个小时.火车在Connecticut的一个地方停了5个小时.

15
00:00:34,654 --> 00:00:36,032
No wonder your neck's bothering you.
难怪你的脖子会疼.

16
00:00:36,508 --> 00:00:37,612
My back would be a mess.
要是我的话，连背也会受不了的.

17
00:00:38,102 --> 00:00:39,507
I told Marie we should have flown.
我跟Marie说我们应该飞回来的.

18
00:00:39,974 --> 00:00:40,890
We should have taken the shuttle.
我们本来就该乘往返巴士的，

19
00:00:41,210 --> 00:00:41,768
But she wouldn't listen.
可她就是不听.

20
00:00:42,146 --> 00:00:43,222
Now I have a pain in the neck.
现在弄得我脖子疼.

21
00:00:43,461 --> 00:00:46,179
Well, you have to admit, the delay wasn't Marie's fault.
Well,不过你得承认，火车延误可不能怪Marie.

22
00:00:46,362 --> 00:00:53,597
Yeah, yeah. I probably shouldn't.
Yeah, yeah. 也许我不应该.

23
00:01:03,203 --> 00:01:04,983
You and Marie are traveling a lot lately.
你和Marie最近经常出去旅游吗?

24
00:01:06,125 --> 00:01:07,844
We're putting the romance back in our marriage.
我们打算把浪漫的感觉重新带回到我们的婚姻生活中来.

25
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:09,969
I'll let you know if it works.
如果这样做真有效果的话, 我会告诉你的.

26
00:01:23,052 --> 00:01:23,625
What did you order?
你点的是什么?

27
00:01:24,603 --> 00:01:25,267
Turkey club.
火鸡三明治.

28
00:01:26,683 --> 00:01:27,166
What did you get?
你拿到的是什么?

29
00:01:28,153 --> 00:01:30,504
Peanut butter and jelly. Bon appetite.
花生酱果冻三明治. 祝你胃口好.

